  "task": "Advanced high-value task: Ontology Mapping Candidate Production Exception Classifier. Scenario: a governance team wants a reproducible analysis that another reviewer can rerun from the row data alone for ontology mapping candidate. Embedded packet: Records: R1 confidence_pct=82 type_compatible=125 cardinality_risk=3; R2 confidence_pct=91 type_compatible=121 cardinality_risk=6; R3 confidence_pct=77 type_compatible=136 cardinality_risk=2. Remediation options: O1 changes confidence_pct by -12% cost=96500; O2 changes type_compatible by -18% cost=109300; O3 changes cardinality_risk by -25% cost=66700; max_budget=135600. Rules and constraints: accept confidence>=85 and type compatible; 65-84 requires curator review; missing values cannot be imputed and all calculations must use only the embedded packet. Required work: quantify the operational consequence of each exception and rank follow-up actions by urgency and evidentiary strength. Deliver ontology_mapping_4.xlsx + expert_memo.md with formulas, intermediate values, row-level citations, explicit assumptions, sensitivity checks, and a final recommendation table. Do not invent inputs; mark ambiguous items as needs_review.",
